RelevantSubjects.Html: You can get into this job through a passenger transport driver intermediate apprenticeship.

You can apply for the Civil Service Fast Track Apprenticeship. This is a 2-year higher apprenticeship. There are 6 different career routes:

  • policy
  • business
  • commercial
  • digital, data and technology
  • finance
  • project delivery

You'll usually need GCSEs but some routes require A levels or equivalent qualifications.
You could take an intermediate apprenticeship in lean manufacturing.
You could train through an advanced apprenticeship as a mortgage adviser.
You may be able to start by completing an actuarial technician higher apprenticeship or actuary degree apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an advanced apprenticeship as an ambulance support worker.

FurtherInfo.Html:
You may be able to train for similar roles, such as air cartographer in the armed forces.

You can find out more information from:

Royal Air Force

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could apply to join the army through an HM forces serviceperson intermediate apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You'll need to apply directly to the army to find the best apprenticeship route for you. This will depend on your qualifications and which service role you're interested in, for example, infantry, artillery or medical.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could complete a network engineer higher apprenticeship or a digital technology solutions degree apprenticeship.

You can complete a rail infrastructure operator or rail engineering operative intermediate apprenticeship.

You can also do a rail engineering technician advanced apprenticeship.
You could do a junior management consultant higher apprenticeship and work your way up as your experience grows.

  • hospitality team member

FurtherInfo.Html: You'll need to apply directly to the army to find the best apprenticeship route for you.

  • advanced apprenticeship as a building services engineering craftsperson

You could also do a composites technician advanced apprenticeship.

You could do a trade union official higher apprenticeship.

You may be able to start by doing a floorlayer intermediate apprenticeship.
You can start by doing a transport planning technician advanced apprenticeship, then move on to a transport planner degree apprenticeship.
You could complete an advanced apprenticeship as a custody and detention officer.
You can do an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in customer service.
You may be able to start training on an operational firefighter advanced apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You'll need to be employed by a fire service to do this.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You may be able to get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship in fashion and textiles, or by doing a garment maker advanced apprenticeship.

You can do a building control surveyor degree apprenticeship.

You could get into this job through a marine engineer advanced apprenticeship.

You can get into this role through a teaching assistant advanced apprenticeship.
You may be able to start on a supply chain practitioner advanced apprenticeship, which could lead onto a supply chain leadership or express delivery manager degree apprenticeship.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can start by doing a hospitality team member intermediate apprenticeship.

You'll also need to show ability in English, maths and IT.

This will usually take 18 months to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time at a college or training provider.

The apprenticeship takes around 4 years and is a mix of academic study and on-the-job training.

You must be supported by your employer to take this route.

  • an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in childcare

FurtherInfo.Html:
If you're aged 16 or over and interested in working in the racing industry, the British Racing School at Newmarket and the National Horseracing College at Doncaster offer pre-apprenticeship foundation courses.

Courses last between 4 and 18 weeks, depending on your experience, and can lead to an apprenticeship in racehorse care and a career as a groom.
